  <text>
    <body>
      <ab type="lido:objectWorkType">Leaflet</ab>
      <ab subtype="creation" type="lido:event">
        <date>1939 after</date>
      </ab>
      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The leaflet features a photograph of the head and arms of a woman. Her head is resting on her arms. The legend below displays the film title in its Serbo-Croatian translation, ‘Predstavnik vlasti’ (in the Russian original: ‘Член правительства’, Member of the government) – a Soviet film.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">The film was directed by Иосиф Хейфиц (Iosif Kheifits) and Александр Зархи (Aleksandr Zarkhi) and was released in 1939.</ab>
